name: Centiskorch VMAX
description: Centiskorch VMAX is the Gigantamax form of Centiskorch, boasting intense firepower and a towering presence on the battlefield.

name: Pikachu VMAX
description: Pikachu VMAX, also known as 'Chonkachu,' features Pikachu in its Gigantamax form, delivering powerful electric attacks.

name: Single Strike Urshifu VMAX
description: Single Strike Urshifu VMAX specializes in delivering powerful, single-hit attacks, embodying the essence of strength.

name: Shadow Rider Calyrex VMAX
description: Shadow Rider Calyrex VMAX combines psychic abilities with ghostly powers, making it a formidable opponent.

name: Mew VMAX
description: Mew VMAX harnesses the DNA of all Pokémon, allowing it to use a variety of attacks with incredible versatility.
